item.title: US-30 West at Bypass US-30
item.description: US-30 West at (Kemmerer) Bypass US-30. Use Bypass US-30 East for Rock Springs; use US-30 West for Cokeville.

item.title: US-189 North at US-30 and US-30 Bypass
item.description: US-189 North at US-30 East to Rock Springs. Continue north on US-189/US-30 West for Kemmerer and Diamondville. US-189 North joins US-30 West to the city center of Kemmerer.

item.title: US-189 North Approaching US-30 and US-30 Bypass
item.description: US-189 North Approaching US-30 and US-30 Kemmerer Bypass

item.title: US-30 East at Bypass US-30
item.description: US-30 East at Bypass US-30 in Kemmerer. Use Bypass US-30 for Rock Springs; use US-30 for US-189 North and Kemmerer.

item.title: US-30 East Approaching Bypass US-30
item.description: US-30 East approaching Bypass US-30, which bypasses Kemmerer. Continue on US-30 for US-189 North.

item.title: US-189 South/US-30 East at US-189/US-30 Split
item.description: US-189 South/US-30 East at US-189/US-30 Split. Turn left for US-30 East onramp to Rock Springs. Continue south on US-189 for Evanston. This is the east end of the Kemmerer US-30 Bypass.

item.title: US-30 East/US-189 South at Split
item.description: US-30 East/US-189 South at US-30 By-Pass and US-30 ramps. Use US-189 South/US-30 East for Evanston. Turn right for the US-30 By-Pass West onramp for Port of Entry and Cokeville.

item.title: I-5 North - Exit305 A-B
item.description: I-5 north approaching Exit 305AB - US-30 By-Pass/Lombard St

item.title: End US-30 By-Pass West at US-30
item.description: End US-30 By-Pass west at US-30. Use US-30 west for Kemmerer. Use US-30 east for Cokeville. US-30 By-Pass loops around the south side of Kemmerer and Diamondville.

item.title: US-30 East/US-189 South at Split
item.description: US-30 East/US-189 South at US-30 By-Pass and US-30 ramps. Use US-189 South/US-30 East for Evanston. Turn right for the US-30 By-Pass West onramp for Port of Entry and Cokeville.

item.title: US-30 West at US-189
item.description: US-30 west at US-189. Use US-189 south for Evanston. Use US-189 North/US-30 West for Diamondville and Kemmerer. US-30 exits the freeway here, while US-30 Bypass continues west around the south side of Kemmerer.

item.title: US-30 West Approaching US-189 and US-30 By-Pass
item.description: US-30 west approaching US-189 and US-30 By-Pass. Continue ahead for US-30 By-Pass towards Cokeville, and Pocatello (Idaho). Exit for US-30 West/US-189 for Kemmerer and Diamondville.
